Partition key — index of the component partition containing this taxon's families:
  cc = Curated Consensus    ch = Curated HMMs
  uc = Uncurated Consensus  uh = Uncurated HMMs
Format: <NCBI tax id> <scientific name>(<partitions>) [<# families in Dfam V1 assigned to this node>]
Note: family counts reflect the full Dfam release; not all partitions may be locally installed.
      Use 'famdb.py check <taxon>' to verify which partitions are present for a given species.

1 root(cc:0,ch:1) [1]
├─2 Order(cc:0,ch:1) [1]
│ ├─4 Genus(cc:0,ch:2) [1]
│ │ └─6 Species(uc:1) [1]
│ └─7 Other Species(uc:1) [1]
└─3 Other Order(cc:0,ch:1) [2]
